Detailed Description

template<class T>
class NT_link_list_o< T >

The empty operation empties an existing queue. The length operation returns the number of elements currently stored in the queue. PURPOSE: A link in a linked list or queue REMARKS: The data fields are public, hence users of this class should not propagate NT_link_list_o pointers
